# Health Guru (C++ Console Application)

## Project Description
Health Guru is a C++ console-based fitness application that provides workout plans
based on user fitness levels and includes a calorie counter feature.

## Features
- User Login
- User Registration
- Workout Plan (Beginner, Intermediate, Advanced)
- Calorie Counter

## File Structure
- main.cpp – Program entry point
- workout.cpp – Workout plan logic
- calorie.cpp – Calorie counter logic

## How to Run
1. Open the project in VS Code
2. Compile using a C++ compiler (g++)
3. Run the executable in terminal

